Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really say that we won?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective work is, by nature, about treating wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our investigations start after there are victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In that sense, we lost before we even started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least we were able to end this lost game in a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to settle for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that talk about the safety of the Sibyl System?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our safe and perfect society is really just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we still live in a dangerous world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In this society, people depend on things that are convenient but also dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our government made us take risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the risks were dispersed and distributed so cleverly that no one was able to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, they did notice, but they pretended that they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone might have been looking the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that it's precisely because these things were so dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that they had to act as if nothing was wrong in order to keep their sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think all the citizens of this town, myself included, were that resourceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to lump people together when I speak, since everyone is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll generalize broadly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think humans in general are resourceful creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can involuntarily try to avoid our responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm rambling.{yep}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm nervous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is what happens next.\N How they're going to judge Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far more difficult and troublesome a task than just shooting a Dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an undeniable fact that he committed crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that we still have that idiot Kagari to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He went down to the basement on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we lose communication with him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one day after the nightmarish riots.{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like dealing with the aftermath of a pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A Psycho-Hazard is a mental disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when it's allowed to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A large number of people needing mental care,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,housing facilities overflowing with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and economic losses due to crippled city functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima was a monstrous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to talk about him in the past tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still the matter of his sentencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The judiciary has been abolished for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so I imagine it'll be quite difficult to prosecute someone based solely on evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting too friendly, Enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been called in by the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The cases Makishima was involved in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will be investigated by a special team formed by the Minister of Welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Public Safety Bureau has no further authority to investigate this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a unique case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical staff need to be present when he is questioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to keep all information strictly confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima Shougo was very likely to have been involved in various crimes in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for the facts to come to light, the Bureau needs to be able to interrogate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any unsolved cases among those past crimes you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima will be disposed of as a research sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, he has been disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have more to worry about at\N Division 1 than an arrested criminal, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An Enforcer escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's still missing.{you jerk}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know if he really escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sibyl System has already been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Enforcer Kagari hasn't been caught by the surveillance network
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's taking care to steer clear of it as he moves about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As it stands, you'll be held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Well...{ew cloves, this bitch.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand an acceptable explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you can talk to me like that?! You're an Enforcer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to discuss our positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who arrested him! It makes no damn sense that we can't even question him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you want to complain, talk to the Chief directly." Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an Enforcer. There's no way in hell they'd let me see the Chief, is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I dare set foot in her office, it's you who'll be in trouble, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There probably isn't anything else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put everything we have into the search for Kagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He could well bring about the end of the Bureau for entirely different reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Chief of the Public Safety Bureau, Ms. Kasei... was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we've met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my appearance has changed quite a bit over the past three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I need to offer you an apology
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding that book I borrowed from you a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up losing it due to unfortunate, though unavoidable, circumstances.{i was sorely tempted to put "a series of unfortunate events" here, but alas}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite difficult to find another copy of that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Touma Kouzaburou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that you were taken in by the Bureau, I felt that it was terribly unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that face... Plastic surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering that body structure, you're a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend Senguji Toyohisa achieved full-body cyberization too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But near-flawless artificial body technology like this isn't available to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell the difference between this body and a human body at all, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the Touma Kouzaburou you know is left except for his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit behind the grotesque serial killings that shook society to its core
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is now the head of the Public Safety Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beyond a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, that's not quite true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only Kasei Joshu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not always Kasei Joshu either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our brains are unitized, so they can be swapped easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We generally take turns using this body.{the bicycle of the MWPSB}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It also serves as a bit of a break from our everyday work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"We," you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm simply a representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just tasked with talking to you here since you and I are old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never shown ourselves to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd say we're pretty well-known by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard of us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,People call us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sibyl System!{dropped.}{dropped}{picked up}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the hell could they say that Kagari just disappeared from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how worked up he got, he wouldn't run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He can calculate how to survive in any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd disappear of his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he was abducted? Kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or he was killed in a way that wouldn't leave any traces of his body behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, with the Decomposer mode of the Dominator or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Tsunemori speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received a report from a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They've found an abandoned, broken Dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's at least twenty kilometers between the Nona Tower and this location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even among all the chaos caused by the riots,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is it really possible that he wasn't caught even once by the cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake that this is Kagari's Dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's damaged quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The built-in GPS isn't functioning either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he break it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid being tracked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this all a ploy by someone who wants us to think exactly that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, just like every other,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you managed to aim straight for the right target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, your friend managed to discover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... the true form of the Sibyl System!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sibyl System is said to use a PDP model—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,an extensive network of supercomputers\N performing parallel distributed processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really a lie, but it's far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Its ability to draw inferences based on a vast knowledge base was not achieved solely by speed gains in conventional computing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Parallelizing the system that was able to do those things and expanding it mechanically
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,simply gave it massive processing ability compared to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, a system that expands and speeds up its ability to think by incorporating human brain activity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was already put into practical use more than fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's precisely because we kept this technology secret and used it carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that today our country is able to function as the only nation on Earth ruled by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even have to destroy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make this public, it'll be the end of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The system currently has 247 constituent members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By having about 200 of the 247\N connected in sessions at any given time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we can continuously monitor and judge the Psycho-Pass of every single person in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechanical programs alone can determine, at most, stress measurements based on the Hue Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Determining Crime Coefficients, which indicate a more profound assessment of human nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,requires a higher degree of thinking ability and judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are the ones who can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we lived in a fair society managed by machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One that didn't depend on flawed human egos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they presented the Sibyl System, and that's why people accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, all those judgments were made arbitrarily by you, an aggregate of human brains?{a braintrust, if you will}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The system is boundlessly fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We judge and supervise people as those who transcend mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The first qualification to be a constituent member of the Sibyl System
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is to have an irregular personality that doesn't fit in with mankind's conventional standards.{in other words, be a hipster}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of aimlessly empathizing with others,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of losing yourself to emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be able to oversee human actions from an outsider's viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That talent is what we require.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, yourself and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also a unique human. One whose Crime Coefficient can't be determined from their Psycho-Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's caused me a great deal of loneliness over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A personality that cannot be measured, even by Sibyl's collective intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is called "criminally asymptomatic."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with this personality are distinguished from all other citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,by their unique ideology and sense of values.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By finding such valuable people and taking them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the system has continued to expand its range of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and gained new possibilities as an intellectual form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why you disappeared instead of being executed after the Bureau took you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was welcomed as a member of the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was confused, but it didn't take long before I was able to understand its true splendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Omnipotence, achieved through expanding both understanding and judgment by sharing one's cognition with other brains...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm a prophet straight out of legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that everything in the world is under my rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are limits to the amount of pleasure a person can obtain in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, pleasure brought out by the intellect is infinite.{yep, hipster}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand that, can't you, Shougo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not really hard to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and I have been isolated and oppressed in this world full of contradictions.{you could say their dreams are attracted to the intrigue that hides it all}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't need to grieve over it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be proud of the nobility of this mission that fate has charged us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has also come for you to take your proper place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're telling me to become a member of the Sibyl System?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intellect and deep insight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,are qualities we eagerly seek out in order to further evolve the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not to say that we can't simply make you a member by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However, "Value exists only in the acts based on one's free will."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were your words, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped that you'd understand my explanation and then agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of being reduced to a cog in a machine isn't very appealing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this would not take away any of your independence as an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, as you can see, I'm still maintaining a sense of my self as Touma Kouzaburou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is say a single word: "Yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation will be completed on our way to the \NMinistry of Welfare using the equipment we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Makishima Shougo known to the public will disappear with your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll become one of those who rule this world and none will be the wiser.{i like how that last part works on several levels}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like the doctor in Balnibarbi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about "Gulliver's Travels" by Swift. Specifically, Part III.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Balnibarbi is the place Gulliver travels to after the flying island of Laputa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor in Balnibarbi comes up with a way to get politicians with conflicting opinions to reconcile with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was surgery in which they'd cut each of their brains in half then have the two hemispheres sewn together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that was done, they could "produce the moderation as well as regularity of thinking."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the self-conceited lot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who think that "they come into the world only to watch and govern its motion,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Swift writes that it is the most desirable approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius at sarcasm, Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not, but Swift certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably thought that I wouldn't resist until I knew where I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but as usual, you weren't very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "on our way to the Ministry of Welfare" earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By saying that, you hinted that we're in transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not inside the Public Safety Bureau, so I judged that I could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be able to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of omnipotence and the pleasure of governing the world...{the pleasure of being governed inside}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like God, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be pleasurable in its own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately I'm not into being an umpire or a referee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't genuinely enjoy the game unless I'm part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love this game that people call "life" from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'd like to continue to participate in it as a player, forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you afraid of dying, even after attaining the omniscience of God?
