Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct in assuming that\N this is Kougami Shinya's number?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I came to know the true form of the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something worth putting your life on the line to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gino! What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been confirmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but the transport aircraft Makishima was on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to have crashed.
